	quest.2417977FCE5FBC2A.title: "Vat Chemistry"
	quest.2798F6913720944D.quest_subtitle: "A Combustion Fuel"
	quest.288CC1F24527EDCA.quest_desc: [
		"To reach the nether without diamonds? Really? "
		""
		"You can make obsidian a few different ways currently, but lava casting a portal is equally as valid of an option!"
		""
		""
		""
		"&o&7Mother, oh mother, I finally realize; to love the whole world I must become a God. "
		""
		"&o&7I will weave them abodes to shield them from the rust of the rain, and flourish their fields to coddle their grains.&r"
	]
	quest.288CC1F24527EDCA.quest_subtitle: "Lava Casting"
	quest.288CC1F24527EDCA.title: "Portal Assembly?"
	quest.28CB7776596C9EB8.quest_subtitle: "Finally, real Andesite!"
	quest.293DBD176B301FBA.quest_subtitle: "Rubber Making"
	quest.29628DF6C3C4E804.quest_desc: [
		"&7&oTODO : PONDER&r"
		""
		"The &6Crogiolo Forge&r, Shortened to &6Forge&r, is the replacement for TFMG's &6Blast Furnace&r; and the first multiblock create machine custom built for this modpack."
		""
		""
		"&l&nBuilding It:&r Place a &6Foundry Blaze&r, surround it with &6Foundry Casings&r to form the base, then build a &b3x4x3&r of &6Foundry Frames&r on top with the bottom layer solid and all subsequent layers hollow. The structure will snap together when complete."
		""
		"&l&nFueling:&r Pipe in &6Honey&r and &6Hot Air&r to ignite the burner; this will actively consume both, but wake up the foundry blaze to her idle state of \"&fWarm&r\" where recipes can be processed. "
		""
		"Higher temperatures require different tiers of &eCinderfuel&r to be piped in at specific times based on what recipe you are making."
		""
		"Each &eCinderfuel&r variety corresponds to a temperature tier: "
		"&aHot&r : &aZesty Cinderfuel&r"
		"&eBlazing&r : &eTart and Tangy Cinderfuel&r"
		"&cSearing&r : &cSpicy and Sweet Cinderfuel&r"
		"&bWhite-Hot&r : &bBerry Cherry Cinderfuel&r"
		"&4Infernal&r : &4Sweltering Cinderfuel&r"
		""
		""
		"&l&nHow to Recipe:&r Toss items into the Well from above or use automation on the walls of the crucible. Each recipe has &btemperature stages&r, a sequence of tiers the forge must reach, for a set duration. The forge ticks through them in order regardless of temperature, but your processing accuracy with heat levels means more &ayield&r per recipe and less waste &cslag&r."
		""
		"&c&lBE CAREFUL&r&c : Failure to satisfy any singular stage of a recipe (Less than &c&l25% accuracy&r&c) will &4&lVOID&r&c the entire recipe, make sure you're automating your Foundry Blaze's inputs properly!&r"
		""
		"Speaking of, you can get a readout of the required stage with a &6Comparator&r."
		""
		""
	]
	quest.29628DF6C3C4E804.quest_subtitle: "Big Mama Blaze"
	quest.29628DF6C3C4E804.title: "Crogiolo Forge"
