	quest.2A77DBAB6DFFE488.quest_subtitle: "The really warm place"
	quest.2A77DBAB6DFFE488.title: "The Nether"
	quest.2D1D720089F4927A.quest_desc: ["Andesite braces are used to construct the frame of your new casings, you will see these used in other recipes as well."]
	quest.2D1D720089F4927A.quest_subtitle: "Strong Supports"
	quest.30F191EE6BA18821.quest_subtitle: "Your First Magnet"
	quest.33B250BF865C6A06.quest_subtitle: "A Combustion Fuel"
	quest.35636EA132BBDEE8.quest_desc: [
		"You'll need a lot of redstone for this."
		""
		""
		"I strongly recommend either a cinder flour + strength potion setup for redstone or wash a bucketload of crushed iron for the chance at getting a few stacks."
		""
		"(ps. you can use a cutting board and a wrench to crush iron earlier than crushing wheels)"
		""
		""
		"You'll be able to harvest huge deposits of redstone soon, for now you'll have to make due."
	]
	quest.35636EA132BBDEE8.quest_subtitle: "Painful"
	quest.35923DE99E1EEADD.quest_desc: ["The Iron you pull from the ground is sufficient for standard applications, but lacks purity needed for steel. Your next objective is to refine iron into a capable material for Steel production. While you don't have total mastery over fluid chemistry or the vats to handle high tier molten metals... Your create machines seem to be eager to refine iron down into a pure granulated dust"]
	quest.35923DE99E1EEADD.quest_subtitle: "An Agonizing Process"
	quest.3A6E59AA90B99B12.quest_desc: [
		"An Optimized Reactor can output a whopping 2.4M SU, Plenty of power for all the EU you'd ever want."
		""
		"At the cost of a lot of material investment, of course."
		""
		""
		"Everything shown in this quest is what you need to &oAssemble a reactor&r it does not account for casings needed for the parts themselves, keep that in mind."
	]
	quest.3A6E59AA90B99B12.quest_subtitle: "Titanic Stress Production"
	quest.3C438C3BCF92D6B1.quest_subtitle: "Power, Finally? "
	quest.3CC265748B4DF058.quest_subtitle: "Steel at Last!"
	quest.3D7151D129FF0276.quest_subtitle: "Metallic Glue"
	quest.42F433BBD4789381.quest_desc: [
		"Add some water in a bucket with your flour to create dough."
		""
		""
		"It's sticky enough to be considered a slime ball, just not green enough."
	]
	quest.42F433BBD4789381.quest_subtitle: "Make it sticky"
	quest.43775477581A2414.quest_desc: ["These sturdy plates will allow the creation of a new type of casing that can handle consistent physical strain"]
	quest.43775477581A2414.quest_subtitle: "Boards for bulking"
	quest.4389066D2B9F140E.quest_desc: [
		"Crafting blueprints allow you to save recipes in world on physical sheets, when you click on them it will automatically craft what you clicked on as long as you have the resources"
		""
		"These are super useful when you're still far from total automation"
	]
	quest.4389066D2B9F140E.quest_subtitle: "Crafting Blueprints"
	quest.451B82B45C00EF86.quest_desc: [
		"Cast Iron will be perfect for the creation of Creosote and Coke in a Coke Oven!"
		""
		"Let's work on making some. You'll need to automate several of them in series to produce enough."
	]
	quest.451B82B45C00EF86.quest_subtitle: "Prepared Iron"
	quest.489A746093E094AC.quest_desc: [
		"You'll want to start producing massive amounts of wheat and sugarcane to procure these."
		""
		""
		"Some helpful tips."
		""
		"Goodluck Firstly."
		"Secondly, you can compress &astraw&r into canvas at a &e2:1&r ratio vs the crafting of &e4:1&r"
		"Thirdly, you can harvest &nstraw automatically with create harvesters&r and applicable plants."
		""
		""
		"The one I personally tested it with was Wheat, there's probably more like Rice if i had to guess."
		""
		""
		"To beat the pack's 100% goal you'll need about &413,500&r of these papers, so try to get them automated as soon as possible!"
		""
		""
		""
		""
		"&o&7Mother oh mother, I get it I get it; This world is mine to discover and document, I will fill scrolls with every known existence in this universe. From the atoms to the animals to the people inhabiting this realm.&r"
	]
	quest.489A746093E094AC.quest_subtitle: "Production Strain"
	quest.4B30FAEE13A9D0FA.quest_desc: [
		"THE NETHER"
		""
		"Your main goals here is to gather nether quartz and a blaze for a blaze burner."
	]
	quest.4B30FAEE13A9D0FA.quest_subtitle: ":3"
	quest.4B30FAEE13A9D0FA.title: "The Nether"
	quest.5191777DC94F6A73.quest_subtitle: "Easy, go punch a tree!"
	quest.5191777DC94F6A73.title: "Acquiring Wood"
	quest.537F0A416650C39D.quest_subtitle: "Gregtech!?!?!?!"
	quest.5580982B2C67888A.quest_desc: [
		"Now that you're starting to settle in comfortably, it's time to start towards your first major goal."
		""
		"The &6Recordkeepers Papyrus&r"
		""
		""
		"However the paper alone is &lway too complex&r to start with, let's ease into things by crafting a couple of &bprecision assemblies&r, these unlock some of the strongest tools in create"
		""
		""
		"Notably the \"&6Factory Gauge&r\" - Which allows you to automate sprawling chains of materials into final products. These Gauges will be a core part of what makes your base shine if you allocate all your production into them."
		""
		""
		"&6Factory Gauges&r are Extremely Flexible and offer multiple playstyles from them existing alone. I'd strongly recommend you experiment with them to get the hang of them"
	]
	quest.5580982B2C67888A.quest_subtitle: "Geared Up and Ready"
	quest.5580982B2C67888A.title: "Precision Mechanism"
	quest.576ED6E650BBF272.quest_subtitle: "Resin Globs"
	quest.57AEDC8C96065F80.quest_desc: [
		"With this, you've overcame the challenge of Automating Steel with Blast Furnaces. Congratulations!"
		""
		""
		"Let's Move onto the next leg of your journey!"
	]
	quest.57AEDC8C96065F80.quest_subtitle: "Congrats!"
	quest.58AEC3478E1FC4A5.title: "Discover a Nether Fortress!"
	quest.59B828D0E89B2A0D.quest_desc: [
		"Redstone, Emeralds, Diamond, Lapis and Ancient Debris no longer spawn naturally."
		""
		"Later in the andesite age you will gain access to mechanical drills that can harvest these materials from ore deposits that are scattered far and wide across the world."
		""
		""
		"Check out EMI for early acquisition methods if you desperately need redstone (hint, wash crushed iron!)"
		""
		"For Diamonds and others, you might be able to loot them and get yourself some better tools early on."
		""
		"Or you know, you can also abuse villager trading, as I did not change anything with Villagers."
	]
	quest.59B828D0E89B2A0D.title: "Ore Changes"
	quest.59F62FD4C9374CB4.quest_desc: [
		"Check out the ponder as it could explain it better than I ever could."
		""
		""
		"But in short, put blaze burners below a copper tank, fuel them, give it water, and stick steam engines on it somewhere to get a massive output of SU."
	]
	quest.59F62FD4C9374CB4.quest_subtitle: "Proper Power"
	quest.5A4C8A467987883D.quest_desc: [
		"Personally, I would watch the ponder for this to get the best idea of how it works."
		""
		""
		"Essentially, you assemble a multiblock pumpjack above an oil spout and then proceed to extract oil from it."
		""
		""
		""
		"Logically, the next step here is distillation, we'll focus on that next."
		""
		""
		""
		"Hope you've got decent steel infrastructure, all these things use a bunch of it!"
	]
	quest.5A4C8A467987883D.quest_subtitle: "A Bit of an Explaination"
	quest.5BF88C8574957810.quest_subtitle: "Mightly Logistics"
	quest.5C666F0B9ADA4164.quest_subtitle: "Item Handling"
